SUMMARY:Butterfly Run w/ Runners Take Action
DESCRIPTION:Northwest Trail Runners\n**Distance**: 3.1 miles\n**Gain**: 42 fluttery feet\n**Start**: [Ladd Circle Park](https://maps.app.goo.gl/bdpBiGRfBgiEQiwU9)\n\nJoin us and Runners Take Action to support our immigrant neighbors as we trace a butterfly through the streets of Portland - a symbol of immigrant rights and dignity.\nAll paces welcome.\n5k - maps provided.\nDonations encouraged.\nLearn more and donate [HERE](https://form-renderer-app.donorperfect.io/give/immigrant-and-refugee-community-organization/butterfly-run?utm_source=online_forms&utm_medium=qr_code&utm_campaign=qr_code)\nLink to route: https://www.strava.com/routes/3468727325692911196\n\nSee you there!\nHosted by: Cheryl\nNorthwest Trail Runners
