SUMMARY:Most of Maple Loop (Trail run in Forest Park)
DESCRIPTION:Northwest Trail Runners\n**Distance**: 6.8 mile trail run\n**Gain**: 900 feet\n**Start**: Lower Saltzman\n**After**: [Pizza Thief ](https://maps.app.goo.gl/nHVNuJERgPj2p2K4A)\n\nDo you like trails\, running in the woods with friends old and new\, and a few hills? Come join us for a frolicking trail run in Forest Park where we will run much of Maple together and provide guidance for anyone who wants to run ALL of Maple (see route links below).\n\nCarpool if you can or park down below. Parking gets tight.\n\n**Link to route**:\nAlmost All of Maple [https://www.strava.com/routes/3349529544885311704](https://www.strava.com/routes/3349529544885311704)\nALL of Maple: [https://www.strava.com/routes/3349530325586518232](https://www.strava.com/routes/3349530325586518232)\n\n**Route description**:\n• Start from Lower Saltzman\n• Left on Maple (then pass Firelane 4 and Koenig AND Leif)\n• Right on Wildwood cutoff\n• Right on Wildwood\n• Right on Saltzman\n• Down Quarry\n• Right on Maple\n• Continue down Saltzman back to the trail head\n\nWe will meet after at:\nPizza Thief\n2610 NW Vaughn St\nPortland\, OR 97210\n\nSee you on the trails!\nHosted by: MACCAM\nNorthwest Trail Runners
